=>JavaScript Script for Voting System:
====Allow secure registration of voters with verification.
====Handle the casting of votes with checks for voter eligibility and uniqueness.
====Use blockchain features to ensure that the votes are immutable and transparent.

>Integration Explanation
>>Setup:
>>>Deploy the restructure.sol smart contract using Hardhat or Truffle.
>>>Use voting.js to interact with the deployed contract.
>>Voter and Candidate Registration:
>>>The Election Commission (deployer) registers candidates and voters using specific addresses and IDs.
>>Voting Process:
>>>Voters can vote by calling the vote() function with the candidate ID.
>>>The smart contract ensures that each voter can vote only once.
>>Result Calculation:
>>>The winningCandidate() function returns the name, party, and vote count of the candidate with the highest votes.
